cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is primarily focused on neural image style transfer, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also discusses the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.AI) and the joint learning of the StyleBank and auto-encoder (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions the real-time processing of images (cs.MM) and the fusion of styles at the region level (cs.GR).
